Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take anything you can spare...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.47,0:02:01.47,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.9\fscx105\fs80\fnMailart Rubberstamp\c&H7A8995&\pos(640,458)}Wolf and the Grand Scheme
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:19.53,Default,TLC,0,0,0,,You're back early.{is this a joke about it being morning now?}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Holo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.81,0:02:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:03:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are three Lumione I managed to collect by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.73,0:03:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The remaining forty-four Lumione are beyond my grasp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing I can think of is to go to a gambling parlor with the money,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,but you'd probably have more luck with that than I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm going to fail, I'd rather put the money to good use.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Owing three more Lumione won't make much of a difference anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm terribly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I just dropped this from the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you sorry for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you have done if I took the money and fled?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.25,0:04:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I failed, I won't be able to fulfill our contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That money would cover your travel expenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You... You're going to give {\i1}me{\i0} money... so I can keep traveling?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:04:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one at fault, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You would have been able to borrow money if not for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you angry at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,How come you're not blaming me for anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You followed me because you were worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.54,0:05:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be angry at you for—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.13,0:05:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a sucker after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A... sucker?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I followed you out of my selfishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You had every right to be mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.04,0:05:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But then you {\i1}apologize{\i0} just because you slapped my hands away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You even came back to say sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I {\i1}was{\i0} sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt like I did something that couldn't be forgiven no matter how many times I apologized.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:06:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I wanted to do all I could,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but it seems that only hurt you more. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me this one question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.85,0:06:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My personality, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Personality? Personality, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,As a male, you have to say that it's because you're in love with me, even if you don't mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.19,0:06:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.32,0:06:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There are times when I want to hear sweet words even if they're a lie,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but once it's too late, hearing those words makes you want to slap the speaker's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Which situation do you think you're in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,T-The latter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you're so softhearted!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:07:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably thought you'd be taking advantage of me if you said something like that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pathetic, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I still do want to hear you say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're special to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,For goodness sake. What are we even doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're the one who made me do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it served as good practice for you, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I must say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, just make me angry. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate the fact that you're a considerate person,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but there are things that can be settled quicker by screaming at each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How much money is in the leather pouch?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Three Lumione and two-sevenths.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That means you still owe forty-three and five-sevenths, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a cunning plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get too excited. I don't know if it's any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. You'll be caught with certainty if you do it the usual way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have an idea of how to get away with it at little risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.71,0:08:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. I'm by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you wanted to discuss something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you asking me to travel along that path?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.28,0:09:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It {\i1}is{\i0} slightly dangerous, but you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Has God not protected you up until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've heard that mercenaries have been sighted around the area recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,God will protect you without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a wonderful shepherd.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all very proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Smuggling? Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.35,0:09:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:10:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're out of your mind. Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there have been many who tried this same plan in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.72,0:10:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,only to be ultimately caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If you know that, our talk should go quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.74,0:10:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,People standing on the brink of ruin can't distinguish a reckless scheme from a perfect one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where you are right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.46,0:10:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I tell you there's a skilled, trustworthy individual who can smuggle the gold?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.94,0:10:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A person that skilled could make plenty of money without resorting to smuggling gold, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds too good to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I said that this person is talented but not making good money?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.82,0:10:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of person could fit the description you've given?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,One who is skilled and employed in this town but is underpaid and in need of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,One who is unhappy because their employer leaves something to be desired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:11:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They're employed by the Church,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.04,0:11:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Church says that smuggling gold is an act of treason.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt they'll accept the job
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.42,0:11:13.15,Default,,1,1,0,,if it gives them an opportunity to frustrate the Church's ends while receiving compensation for their work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The odds of betrayal are also close to zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll be as convinced as I am when you hear the name of this person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, why don't you smuggle gold yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:33.33,Default,,1,1,0,,Why would you tell me about the idea when you know that your share will become smaller as a result?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The payment deadline for my debt is today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be incarcerated by the trading house at sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've managed to gather only this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it as collateral and put your trust in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I request that the repayment be deferred,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.01,0:11:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and I also need you to invest your assets in the purchase of gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you have the luxury of wavering?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.41,0:12:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,One of your men just left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.99,0:12:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I have ears that are keen enough to unearth the deepest secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The men downstairs are planning to escape this sinking ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.93,0:12:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Another one just left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, it's only a matter of days before this shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Mr. Lemerio{*Lemerio-san}, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You must know someone who can trade the smuggled gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you help us execute this plan on relatively favorable terms to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Mr. Lemerio{*Lemerio-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,May God forgive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Call Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think a good-natured man like you could pull one over on that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There are innocent people in this world who prefer good-natured men.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.64,0:13:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You certainly talk a lot for someone who doesn't know anything about females.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You just drove Lemerio into a corner for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me deal with her on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who ended up with worthless goods due to my own greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If I have you convince her so I can avoid feeling guilty, that means I'm hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:54.55,Default,,1,1,0,,Curses! And here I thought I'd be able to add to the list of favors I've done for you and cash them in later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew! That was a close one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Mr. Lawrence{*Lawrence-san} and... {*}Miss Holo{*Holo-san}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be the will of God for us to meet in front of the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I'm not that easily fooled.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:26.08,Default,,1,1,0,,Thank heavens. I've heard that lately there are those at services who have drunk too much of the Holy Blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't drink much, so I only take a little bit of the wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have something you'd like to...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.01,0:14:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'd like to offer you a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's find a place to sit down and talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's to our reunion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.08,0:15:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Norah{*Norah-san}, you said you could travel as far as Lamtra, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you even bring your flock along?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If there aren't too many.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to hire you for a slightly unusual job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be paid twenty Lumione,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and it won't be in the form of a banknote.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pay in cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Did you say twenty?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, twenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be on contingency due to the risks involved, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If you fail, you won't receive anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Your job is to venture out with your sheep and return them safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You only need to do what you normally would as a shepherd.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be a dangerous task
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're willing to pay twenty Lumione.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.47,0:15:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't deny that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:16:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't force you to accept, and I'm willing to let you think it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Guild membership fees are one Lumione at most, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.93,0:16:12.36,Default,,1,1,0,,With twenty, you'll be able to rent a house and take care of your daily expenses, working without worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.01,0:16:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,When the time comes, you'd even be able to obtain a business permit with ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.19,0:16:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you'd be the mistress of Norah Dressmakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Norah{*Norah-san}, had you planned to join the tailor's guild in this city?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.99,0:16:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I was thinking about another town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But the sprawling size of this city is appealing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be difficult to live in an unfamiliar town with no friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but you probably want to get away from the Church in this city, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,T-That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The harder you work to protect the sheep that the church entrusts you with,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the more they suspect you of using pagan witchcraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.58,0:17:08.57,Default,,1,1,0,,They send you to places ordinary shepherds would never tread for the sake of revealing your true identity,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,by claiming that safer territories are occupied by other shepherds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:21.01,Default,,1,1,0,,I imagine that they intend to keep sending you to dangerous\Nplaces until you're attacked by wolves or mercenaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll do this day after day until they find evidence of your heathen nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a victim of a similar situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me state it clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The Church of this town is lower than swine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.07,0:17:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why we came up with a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll cause a little trouble for the Church, make some money, and leave for another town.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.21,0:17:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you plan to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Smuggle gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:17:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How will I be involved in this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.77,0:18:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll hide the gold inside the stomachs of your sheep in order to pass the checkpoints of this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell me the rest of plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The price of gold is extremely high in every town under the influence of the Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.24,0:18:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why the ideal place to get it is in the pagan town of Lamtra.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All of the safe roads leading to Lamtra are crowded with people,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and it has been the territory of other shepherds for ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.18,0:18:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be able to travel through desolate roads without being suspected of any wrongdoing,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and that route is also the shortest distance between Lamtra and this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:19:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being mistreated by the Church, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This plan serves as an ideal opportunity to take revenge against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.32,0:19:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The Church's two biggest sources of income are tithes and the gold trade, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.84,0:19:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we're caught, the punishments will be heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And once the job is done, you'll have to leave this town to be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The reward is twenty Lumione.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.89,0:19:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Please allow me to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be my pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.37,0:19:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Likewise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have accepted if someone else had approached me with the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:20:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided to do it because it was you, {*}Mr. Lawrence{*Lawrence-san}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you be happier about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.45,0:20:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything went perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.05,0:20:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care how great the profit—nothing exists to balance out the wager of a person's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And just talking up the profit like that is little different from fraud.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Merchants always say that if you get bamboozled into a bad contract, you're the fool at fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.59,0:20:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But who's the person we're dealing with here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She's only a shepherd girl who doesn't know how the world works.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that the girl's smile looked innocent enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.26,0:20:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, you're far too kind for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.89,0:21:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That little girl is not a mere lamb who exists just to be hunted and eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a brave sheep who's decided to mingle with the predators.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.45,0:21:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She might even be a different animal wearing sheep's skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to admit it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.17,0:21:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but she's a shepherd that even I approve of.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not in the wrong here,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.09,0:21:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,so try to put others before you a bit less often.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, I have to do everything I can so that we all end up laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.43,0:21:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it not be better for just the two of us to have the last laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.52,0:21:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind that either,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.19,0:21:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'd prefer if we could all be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.61,0:21:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.71,0:21:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, are you really going to go through with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.00,0:22:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.88,0:22:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.42,0:22:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a choice, Liebert!
